  <context>
    <background>
      Task 018's factory edit was high-leverage: 7 dict entries eliminated 112 failures by
      resolving 2 startup-time error signatures. Task 018's cluster-impact report
      (`baseline/post-018-passing-delta-2026-05-31.md`) lists 17 clusters fully eliminated.
      Task 008's scope-extension annotations on those POMLs are now stale.

      This task is a small, focused refresh — not a redesign. Phase 2+3 task scopes are largely
      correct as-is; what's needed is updating the per-task failure counts and marking
      no-longer-applicable cluster annotations as resolved.

      Parse approach: same as task 008 — PowerShell/Bash XPath on the TRX `&lt;UnitTestResult outcome="Failed"&gt;`
      elements, group by namespace prefix. The TRX is committed (~12 MB but gitignored, on disk).
    </background>
